long_desc.thetext:
Tracker for async updates of golang-github-golang-appengine for rawhide and other fedora distribution.
As golang devel packages are used only as a build-time dependency at the moment, this tracker keeps updates and other information about this package, e.g. broken dependencies, exceptions, important pieces of information and other issues.

Package golang-github-golang-appengine-0-0.3.git1c3fdc5.fc23: * should fix your issue, * was pushed to the Fedora 23 testing repository, * should be available at your local mirror within two days. Update it with: # su -c 'yum update --enablerepo=updates-testing golang-github-golang-appengine-0-0.3.git1c3fdc5.fc23' as soon as you are able to. Please go to the following url: https://admin.fedoraproject.org/updates/FEDORA-2015-12481/golang-github-golang-appengine-0-0.3.git1c3fdc5.fc23 then log in and leave karma (feedback).
